name: Suspender Skirt + Leggings
description:
This is the cutest thing ever!! Vintage / Modern Style.

Suspender Skirt!!! 
One size fits all 6 month - 3 years ( Check measurements because I think it will fit older in some small children )
The suspenders are completely removable, So If you want to change the look easy peasy!

Soft, Airy cotton material.
15" Un- stretched
38" Max stretch

7" Length

the straps have 2 press studs for different height variations one at 20" and another at 22". 

The Suspender skirt is pictured with our New style Stretch leggings, Available in the Fashion section x

Super soft and stretchy Leggings.

Love to mix it up with a funky pattern skirt or dress, Plain leggings are the best!

The leggings come in sizes 
6-18months - 15 ' waist 
2-3 years - 20' waist
3-4 years - 22" waist

They are all elastic waisted and have an extra stretch of about 3 inches.

name: Farm Treasure - Sling Pouch
description:
Such a beautiful Fabric - 100% Organic.

Handmade fabric/leather Strap sling pouch.
Pouch is button up and perfect for holding fine jewellery and lip gloss or metal cars and sticks for the spider cage!!


Sling pouches are sized differently, 8 X 5 Inches in size and the strap is 15 inches long. Being the largest. Great for throwing over the shoulder of all ages.
